        values = new ContentValues(); values.put(COL_NAME, "Warcraft 3 The Frozen Throne (PC)");	values.put(COL_GENRE, "Fantasy, Strategy, RTS");	values.put(COL_RELEASE, "2003-07-01");	values.put(COL_BLURB, "Experience the next chapter in the Warcraft Saga! Warcraft III: The Frozen Throne is the official expansion pack to Warcraft III: Reign of Chaos. Many months have passed since Archimonde and the Burning Legion were defeated at the Battle of Mount Hyjal. For each race, The Frozen Throne adds several new units and buildings, including a player-controlled shop, and one new hero per race. The population limit has been increased from 90 to 100. In addition, The Frozen Throne re-introduces naval battles, which were almost completely absent in Warcraft 3. Although generally only available in the campaign, naval units can be placed using the World Editor and can be purchased from certain buildings in melee maps.");	db.insert(GAME_TBL_NAME, null, values);
